OL,5, One of the country's top schools has   
OL,6, launched an investigation after former 
OL,7, footballer Fabrice Muamba said his son 
OL,8, faced racist abuse in a school rugby   
OL,9, game.                                  
OL,11,FMr Muamba tweeted that his 12-year-old 
OL,12,Fson "received monkey chants" from      
OL,13,Fopponents at Manchester Grammar School 
OL,14,Fafter scoring a try.                   
OL,16,F"Racism is learnt; be careful what you 
OL,17,Fare teaching your children," he said.  
OL,19,FThe school said it condemned racism and
OL,20,Fwould "take the appropriate action".   
